{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"11":{"eng-name":"The Rites of Hajj (Kitab Al-Manasik Wa'l-Hajj)","ara-name":"كتاب المناسك"}},"section_detail":{"11":{"hadithnumber_first":1721,"hadithnumber_last":2045,"arabicnumber_first":1721,"arabicnumber_last":2045}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1760,"arabicnumber":1760,"text":"حدثنا القعنبي، عن مالك، عن ابي الزناد، عن الاعرج، عن ابي هريرة، ان رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم راى رجلا يسوق بدنة . فقال \" اركبها \" . قال انها بدنة . فقال \" اركبها ويلك \" . في الثانية او في الثالثة","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (1689) Sahih Muslim (1322)"}],"reference":{"book":11,"hadith":40},"chapter":{"id":18,"ara-name":"باب فِي رُكُوبِ الْبُدْنِ","eng-name":"On Riding The Sacrificial Animals","isFirstHadith":true}}]}